2102:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-boot/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * Gets data from the receive FIFO. \n\n
2103:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-boot/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * Receive FIFO should be read only if data is availble in the FIFO. This can be checked using
2104:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-boot/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * the API XMC_USIC_CH_RXFIFO_IsEmpty(). Receive FIFO error flag will be set if an attempt is made
2105:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-boot/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * to read from an empty receive FIFO. To read all the received data, user should keep reading data
