2138:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-boot/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  *
2139:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-boot/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * \par<b>Description</b><br>
2140:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-boot/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * Checks if receive FIFO is full. \n\n
2141:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-boot/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * When the receive FIFO filling level reaches the configured size, FIFO full flag is set.
2142:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-boot/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * Any data received when the receive FIFO is full, is lost.
2143:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-boot/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  *
2144:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-boot/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_usic.h ****  * \par<b>Related APIs:</b><BR>
