 514:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-boot/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_dma.h ****  * and returns "false" if it is. In addition, it also checks if the clock is gated
