 685:D:/Infineon/Tools/DAVE IDE/4.5.0.202105191637/eclipse/workspace/XMC4300-boot/Libraries/XMCLib/inc\xmc_dma.h ****  * Should an overrun occur, the bit corresponding to the used DLR line is set. The
